overview:
Frances Hunt is an online furniture retailer that has sold high quality furniture UK wide since 1954. Their expertise in the furniture industry has resulted in a well-selected range of products that suits the needs and styles of their customers nationwide.

Their wide product range covers a cacophony of different interior styles from whole bedroom, and dining room sets that can be bought complete or individually to living room and children’s bedroom furniture, there is something to suit almost every room style imaginable at Frances Hunt.

Their distribution centre is based in Essex and their delivery services boast excellence including a white glove service where their products are not only delivered but also assembled and placed in the customer’s exact required space – excellent for those who have difficulties that prevent them from manually labouring over a new product arrival.

Visit Frances Hunt’s website to find out more about what they offer.
